): 555\xe2\x80\x93572. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.2307%2F256693">10.2307/256693</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACounterproductive+work+behavior&amp;rft.atitle=A+typology+of+deviant+workplace+behaviors%3A+A+multidimensional+scaling+study&amp;rft.au=Bennett%2C+R.+J.&amp;rft.aufirst=S.+L.&amp;rft.aulast=Robinson&amp;rft.date=1995&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.issue=2&amp;rft.jtitle=Academy+of+Management+Journal&amp;rft.pages=555-572&amp;rft.volume=38&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F256693&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-4"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">Skarlicki, D. P.; Folger, R. (1997). "Retaliation in the workplace: The roles of distributive, procedural, and interactional justice". <i>Journal of Applied Psychology</i>. <b>82</b> (3): 434\xe2\x80\x93443. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1037%2F0021-9010.82.3.434">10.1037/0021-9010.82.3.434</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACounterproductive+work+behavior&amp;rft.atitle=Retaliation+in+the+workplace%3A+The+roles+of+distributive%2C+procedural%2C+and+interactional+justice&amp;rft.au=Folger%2C+R.&amp;rft.aufirst=D.+P.&amp;rft.aulast=Skarlicki&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.jtitle=Journal+of+Applied+Psychology&amp;rft.pages=434-443&amp;rft.volume=82&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1037%2F0021-9010.82.3.434&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>\n<li id="cite_